# Calendar & Meeting Reminders

## Product truth

- **Hub `/app/meetings`** ships Phase A schedule + R1 Events/RSVP (not a full union calendar grid)
- **Transactional SMTP** is opt-in (`EMAIL_ENABLED` + ADR-016) for officer self-reminders, invite accept links, and opt-in RSVP confirm — **no marketing / member broadcast lists**
- **`/app/overdue`** tracks **grievance CA step deadlines only** — not membership meetings
- **No `/member` portal** — live RSVP is public token form `/r/[token]`

Full spec: [`docs/modules/CALENDAR_MEETINGS.md`](../../docs/modules/CALENDAR_MEETINGS.md)

## Two surfaces (do not conflate)

| Surface | Auth | Meeting scope | Persistence |
|---------|------|---------------|-------------|
| **Officer Hub** | Login + MFA + module RBAC | Grievance `ScheduledMeeting` **or** membership `LocalMeetingSchedule` / `UnionMeeting` | Memory default; Postgres via `*_DB_BACKEND` |
| **Public Comms** | None (client-only) | Announcement + offline RSVP exports | None — export PNG/PDF/doc/xlsx/ics only |
| **Public RSVP** | Token only | `UnionMeeting` + `RsvpResponse` | `MEETINGS_RSVP_DB_BACKEND` (memory default) |

**Terminology guard:** grievance "Meeting scheduler" ≠ monthly membership / LEC events.

**Three email/reminder builders (locked):** (1) public Comms invite `event-email.ts`, (2) Hub R2 copy draft `membership-meeting-reminder.ts`, (3) R3 SMTP self-remind — see `docs/audit/current-ground-truth.md`. Do not merge (1) and (2).

## Shipped today

### Phase A — local schedule
- `LocalMeetingSchedule`, `/app/meetings` schedule settings, banner, `/meetings/[slug]`, recurrence math

### R0 / R0.5 — offline + Comms invite email
- Document Generator hybrid LEC RSVP pack + Board Notice `InviteEmailPanel`

### R1 — tokenized RSVP
- `UnionMeeting` / `RsvpToken` / `RsvpResponse`, Hub Events board, `/r/[token]`, tallies (quorum = yes any joinMode; food = on-site yes + guests), CSV export, walk-in entry
- Do **not** reuse grievance `ScheduledMeeting`

### R2 light / R3
- Banner can show quorum/food for upcoming events
- Copy-only `membership_meeting_reminder` draft on Hub Events board
- `src/lib/email/send.ts` (nodemailer) when `EMAIL_ENABLED=true`

