## Agent alignment

1. Grievance ≠ membership — separate entities and APIs
2. Public = less detail; token RSVP ≠ member portal
3. No marketing email; audit every transactional send
4. Prefer Postgres flag for durable RSVP campaigns; memory has Hub durability banner

## Do Not

- Auto-broadcast to member lists
- Conflate grievance meetings with membership events
- Build `/member` portal for RSVP
- Put event invite email on grievance draft APIs
